parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the transmission fluid leaks
the transmission makes a loud noise
the vehicle shakes or vibrates
the transmission fails to engage into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission pin can cause the transmission to lock up, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission pin falls out
the transmission locks up
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the transmission fluid leaks
the transmission makes a loud noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the shift interlock can cause the vehicle to shift out of park without the brake pedal being depressed, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle shifts out of park without the brake pedal being depressed
the vehicle rolls or moves without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the air bag warning indicator can cause concern and distraction for the driver, potentially leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The air bag warning indicator illuminates on the dashboard
sometimes intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air bags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The air bags fail to deploy in the event of a crash
sometimes resulting in injuries or fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air bag clock spring can cause the air bag warning indicator to illuminate and potentially lead to air bag failure in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The air bag warning indicator illuminates
and the clock spring may need to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the horn and cruise control can cause inconvenience and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The horn and cruise control fail to function
sometimes accompanied by the air bag warning indicator illumination.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the serpentine belt can cause the loss of power steering, water pump, and alternator functions, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The serpentine belt comes off
resulting in loss of power steering
water pump
and alternator functions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the EGR valve can cause the check engine light to come on, leading to failed smog checks and potential engine damage.
symptoms: The check engine light comes on
and the vehicle fails smog checks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the 2.7L engine can cause the engine to seize, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine seizes
resulting in loss of power and control.
